      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "什么原因？什么原因？……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "现在，是什么原因都没有关系了，现在已没有原因了，现在，你和我已不再有任何关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "死人，是不会和任何人有关系的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你……你本来难道又和我有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "无论什么关系，现在都已过去了。现在我想为你做的事全部已经做完了，你还是……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "我还是不懂，你越说我越不懂。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你根本不必懂。你和我已全无关系。从此以后，你再也休要想起我，我也不会想起你，因为……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只因死人是不会再记住任何人的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "蒋笑民上次人宫，就是从我这里逃出去的，从这窗子。这宫中只有这窗子能逃出去。他……他在我这里养好了伤，就从窗口跳下。窗外是海水……温柔的海水，永远不会伤害任何人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "我早已猜出必定是你救了他。你一生都活在寂寞中，所以，你见着他，就将心交给了他。",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "他本是个值得女子将心交给他的男人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "不错，他是个好男儿，但……但……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "但你还年轻，你为什么不好好地活下去？你……你为什么不？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只因我的心已被他带走了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你已决定了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我已决定了。至于你……你也从这窗子里走吧！这白水宫，并没有什么值得你逗留之处。这里有的只是悲哀、忧伤、寂寞……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "我现在又多懂了一些。蒋笑民要我将书信交给你，除了要你见我外，也是算准我会和他一样被困在这里，所以指点我一条生路逃走，是么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "也许是，也许不是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "无论是不是，我都不能走。除了我定要见到宫主这原因外，我还发觉这白水宫中竟似隐藏着许多有关我的秘密……我实在想不出这白水宫怎么隐藏着有关我的秘密，我一定要查出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你已经决定了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "我已决定了！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "我为什么要后悔？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "因为真相常常是残酷的，真实常常会刺伤人。但你既已决定了，你就去吧，这里有一条路，可直接通向白水娘的寝宫。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "从这里走，你就可见着白水娘了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "多谢关照，多蒙指点，总之，一切都多谢了，在下就此别过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你莫要谢我，我也有件事求你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你若不答应，也就算了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "无论什么事，但请吩咐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我心里有个疑问，只有你才能给我回答。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你不能解释的事，只怕我也不能。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你能的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "那……那是有关哪方面的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "武功？你也对武功有意？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "从我有知识的那天起，我就在想，天下的武功中不知道有没有一招是任何人都不能抵挡的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "这……这问题只怕任何人都不能回答。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，这问题的确难以答复，何况我终年都生活在这小楼里，世上纵然有这样的一招，我也不知。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "世上武功流派极多，其中自然不乏极厉害的杀手，但这些杀手纵能称雄于一时，却都未能真的横扫天下，何况纵然它能纵横天下，也不能就此证明那是绝对没有任何人能抵挡的。这道理你可明白？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我明白，因为这'绝对没有'四个字已不是任何人所能证实。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "所以我日日夜夜地想，我想出了许许多多的招式，但这些招式不用去问别人，我自己就已能抵挡了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "后来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "后来我遇着蒋笑民，在他养伤的时候，我就要他将他所知道的一切武功招式完全都告诉我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "此人不但聪明绝顶，而且出生于武林世家，天下各门各派的武功招式，他的确可算知道得不少。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "他告诉我的招式，有些和我自己创出的差不多，但也有些是完全不同的。他走了后，我就试着将这些招式全都融会贯通，看看是否能取其精华，创出一招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "经过一年多昼夜不停的思索，我终于创出了一招，我确信这一招必定是天下武功门派都没有的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你怎么证实此点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "因为世上若有这一招，这一招必定是早已名震天下，蒋笑民也必定早已知道，因为，他们知道的武功杀手，我轻易便可抵挡，但这一招，这一招却是我自己苦思半年后也无法抵挡的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "这一招想来必定妙极。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "但我虽不能抵挡这一招，却也不能就此证明别人也不能抵挡，所以，我更急着等你来，只因世上若有能证明此招的人，这人就是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "为什么是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "因为我已听说你几乎已经是当今天下的第一高手，你若也不能抵挡这一招，能抵挡的人必定很少了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你对世上任何事情都已不再关心，为什么还要急着证实这一招？莫非你想将这一招用在别人身上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "也许是，也许不是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你想将这一招用在谁身上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这个……你管不着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "莫非是白水娘？因为你恨她入骨？你为什么恨她？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你既已答应我，为什么还要问这么多？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "你的剑在哪里？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "这算什么招式？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "就是这一招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "但这一招根本伤不了我……这一招根本连任何人都伤不了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "正因为这一招已先立于必不能胜之地，所以别人才不能抵挡，因为任何人只怕都没有瞧过这样的招式。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "但这招根本不必抵挡……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "谁说不必抵挡？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "这……这根本不必说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好，那么你瞧着。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑纱女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这一招不是根本不用抵挡的么？你为何要躲？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_hei_sha_nv",
      "text": "好厉害，好厉害……如今我才瞧出了这一招的厉害。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 546,
